{"tid":1918862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謝緑卡：警方光明正大執法不用道歉","createTime":"2020-03-10T11:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T11:26:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69fe595925c7244f734f3c549631e953bf2d38e2","tid":1918862,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1513595_1_20200310183243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1513595_1_20200310183243.jpg&h=656ae7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多名葵青區議員關注區內發生的警民衝突，質疑警方執法使用暴力不合理。葵青警區指揮官謝振中表示，不同意警暴的指控，強調警方執法時必定是有暴力事件發生。<br />\n<br />\n有區議員不滿防暴警員日前在將軍澳要求路過的市民向警員道歉，才准放行，要求謝振中道歉。謝振中回應說，警方光明正大執法，不用道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513595-20200310.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513595-20200310.htm&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSn%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=facdc8e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513595-20200310.htm&h=e2d5be7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513595-20200310.htm</a>"},{"pid":"912ba669416e79e6326c2845744e121f7e9b626d","tid":1918862,"uid":35802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦謝振中！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6a61166518f878d5c321753211f883e6ac6b3b","tid":1918862,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"執法包括要求道歉？<br />\n你覺得要求道歉係執法嘅一部分？"}]}